        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle BEFORE: Traditional Perimeter-Based Network (Implicit Trust)\n\ncloud \&quot;Internet\&quot; {\n}\n\nnode \&quot;Perimeter Firewall\&quot; {\n}\n\nnode \&quot;Citrix / VPN Portal\\n(Single-Factor Authentication)\&quot; {\n}\n\nrectangle \&quot;Internal Network (Flat / Weak Segmentation)\&quot; {\n\n  node \&quot;Billing Systems\&quot; {\n  }\n\n  node \&quot;Claims Processing Systems\&quot; {\n  }\n\n  node \&quot;Clinical Databases\&quot; {\n  }\n\n  node \&quot;File Servers\&quot; {\n  }\n\n  node \&quot;Admin &amp; Identity Services\&quot; {\n  }\n}\n\n\&quot;Internet\&quot; --&gt; \&quot;Perimeter Firewall\&quot;\n\&quot;Perimeter Firewall\&quot; --&gt; \&quot;Citrix / VPN Portal\\n(Single-Factor Authentication)\&quot;\n\&quot;Citrix / VPN Portal\\n(Single-Factor Authentication)\&quot; --&gt; \&quot;Internal Network (Flat / Weak Segmentation)\&quot;\n\n\&quot;Billing Systems\&quot; -- \&quot;Claims Processing Systems\&quot;\n\&quot;Claims Processing Systems\&quot; -- \&quot;Clinical Databases\&quot;\n\&quot;Clinical Databases\&quot; -- \&quot;File Servers\&quot;\n\&quot;File Servers\&quot; -- \&quot;Admin &amp; Identity Services\&quot;\n\nnote right of \&quot;Internal Network (Flat / Weak Segmentation)\&quot;\nImplicit trust once authenticated\nUnrestricted east-west movement\nLarge blast radius\nend note\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="O5r-G8Le8r-0ViniO0w3-1">
